data.description: A wonderful 3 bedroom 2.5 bath brick rancher in the country but close to Chestertown and Middletown for tax free shopping. It sits on about  2.4 acres of a rolling lot that goes down to the community pond and picnic area. It has an instant hot water system, a relatively new septic system, roof and other amenities.  It is close to the schools and currently has school bus service on the street.  The street ends at a cul de sac. This is the place for you . There is the potential for a qualified buyer to assume a very low interest VA loan.
